{"tid":1035132,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2019 DSE既入一入泥","createTime":"2019-02-24T12:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T16:16:29.000Z","uid":90125,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52158a8e3a783c0ed526910225b573266b63e72b","tid":1035132,"uid":90125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:07:31.000Z","msg":"好多人會問究竟係咪一定要考好DSE先可以有更好的命運？<br />\n究竟我考DSE係咪真係要放棄所有自己的興趣？<br />\n究竟DSE對我地泥講係咪真係咁重要？<br />\nDSE就代表一切？<br />\n我當然心諗答案：「唔係」<br />\n開始唔想溫書 想即時發掘返自己既興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到左今日 我似乎又有另一番睇法<br />\n係 冇錯<br />\nDSE係折磨學生 殘忍既一個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢個就係現實 <br />\n香港社會逼你一定要面對<br />\n自問 我都唔想成為一個只係識讀書 操paper <br />\n日日只要係自修室流連的人<br />\n我相信冇人會想<br />\n但係 係你放棄之前 <br />\n你有冇諗過你會辜負自己既家人、老師對你既期望呢？<br />\n你做呢個決定前又有冇諗過自己真係會取得成功？<br />\n要知道 係香港：<br />\n你攞唔到最基本既「入場卷」<br />\n出到社會根本冇人會睇得起你<br />\n到時候你又會點睇自己？ <br />\n你屋企人會點睇你？<br />\n佢地對你既期望 將會完完全全變左失望<br />\n呢場既戰爭 <br />\n唔單止係為你自己而戰<br />\n仲有你既屋企人 你既老師等等等人<br />\n所以唔好放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有一個月時間 好好捱埋佢<br />\n2019 DSE加油！"},{"pid":"d0630bc655eb224f20d6036b47d62a857e71e4cb","tid":1035132,"uid":35572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:08:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061bd932cde242f3715f9717de6e7d18e13a71d4","tid":1035132,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"入泥？<br />\n<br />\n入下白泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c9541e6a4f97e10b66de30ba6ad24aa22c9a948","tid":1035132,"uid":66099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:19:22.000Z","msg":"你老師理撚得你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打份工啫，你畢完業又bye bye下一班"},{"pid":"102908f1f3d95885e045d59ec15df12b1d1435b4","tid":1035132,"uid":10133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:14:38.000Z","msg":"泥你老母"},{"pid":"a2d93b58b410fe2cc57800489a16c9aec31368eb","tid":1035132,"uid":238824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"061bd932cde242f3715f9717de6e7d18e13a71d4","tid":1035132,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T12:16:59.000Z","msg":"入泥？<br />\n<br />\n入下白泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"53da6a14d83d024b123e795c0706126de78f8237","tid":1035132,"uid":238824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾band 1尾學校predict 五科19，諗緊報asso定lingu bba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b157eb17edb167b5bd8e2f2dff011b45572f95","tid":1035132,"uid":90125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53da6a14d83d024b123e795c0706126de78f8237","tid":1035132,"uid":238824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"垃圾band 1尾學校predict 五科19，諗緊報asso定lingu bba<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:35:51.000Z","msg":"點都博一博先 lingu bba <br />\n信自己 有目標就得<br />\n加油啊ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f67930b5a1fd633d4a8916b5801bd88f43db27","tid":1035132,"uid":16775,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:37:25.000Z","msg":"泥你老母呀 炒中文啦仆街 書都唔搵走黎上連登"},{"pid":"55467e8a20671d2d08ea7a2e4eb859b33d6fa057","tid":1035132,"uid":16775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f67930b5a1fd633d4a8916b5801bd88f43db27","tid":1035132,"